page.title: 10THE PEOPLE
page.content: Although our area is supposed to be sparsely populated there still seems to be a lot of people about. There are people of all ages; young, middle aged and the older generation. Some of the older men can be seen on their bikes. They probably had bikes when they were young and used to cycle about before there were many cars. They wear black jackets, flat caps and cycle clips. There are lots of children about too. Many young couples have moved out here because houses are cheaper and they've brought their children with them. Lots of people drive into Norwich or Yarmouth to work. There are also lots of people who have lived here for years and years. Whether they are locals or newcomers, the children and adults of the area are very friendly.
